<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>Class<sp/>|<sp/>Purpose<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|-------|---------|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`SpawnAmountProvider`<sp/>|<sp/>Abstract<sp/>interface<sp/>for<sp/>calculating<sp/>spawn<sp/>quantity<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`FixedSpawnAmount`<sp/>|<sp/>Always<sp/>returns<sp/>a<sp/>fixed<sp/>count<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
